ortz\n| first            = Martha Ellen\n| chapter          = Where or When Was Your Servant Innocent?\n| editor1-last     = Bunge\n| editor1-first    = Marcia J. \n| title            = The Child in Christian Thought\n| publisher        = Eerdmans\n| year             = 2001\n| chapter-url      = https://books.google.com/?id=QBrHz8gRRowC&pg=PA93\n| isbn             = \n| ref = harv\n}}\n* {{Cite book\n| last             = Wiley\n| first            = Tatha\n| title            = Original Sin: Origins, Developments, Contemporary Meanings\n| publisher        = Paulist Press\n| year             = 2002\n| url              = https://books.google.com/books?id=eUVrj1R8f2oC&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage&q&f=false\n| isbn             = 9780809141289\n| ref              = harv\n}}\n*{{cite book\n| last1            = Wright\n| first1           = David F.\n| chapter          = Mary\n| editor1-last     = McKim  \n| editor1-first    = Donald K. \n| editor2-last     = Wright\n| editor2-first    = David F.\n| title            = Encyclopedia of the Reformed Faith\n| publisher        = Westminster John Knox Press\n| year             = 1992\n| url              = https://books.google.com/?id=MJPsgwN789gC&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage&q&f=false\n| isbn             = 9780664218829\n| ref              = harv\n}}\n\n* {{Cite book\n| last             = Coyle\n| first            = Kathleen \n| title            = Mary in the Christian Tradition: From a Contemporary Perspective\n| publisher        = Gracewing Publishing\n| year             = 1996\n| url              = https://books.google.com/?id=5QCZlA_j3BcC&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage\n| isbn             = 9780852443804\n| ref              = harv\n}}\n* {{Cite book\n| last             = Mullett\n| first            = Michael A.\n| title            = The Catholic Reformation\n| publisher        = Psychology Press\n| year             = 1999\n| url              = https://books.google.com/?id=1RRKrNCB5_8C&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage\n| isbn     